Code 
data_iris %>% 
  group_by(Species) %>%
  summarise("n" = n(),
            "M_SL" = mean(Sepal.Length),
            "M_PL" = mean (Petal.Length)) %>%
  flextable() %>%
  italic(part = "header", j = 2:4) %>%
  set_header_labels("M_SL" = "M (Sepal Length)") %>%
  set_header_labels("M_PL" = "M (Petal Length") %>%
  autofit()
